info.title: Bot ajouté sur un serveur, config
Private Voice-Chats
info.description:
Create a private voice-chat (aka Temp-Chat).
User can set userlimit and can NOT change the channel name.
And if you dont wanna have 100 of channels, then you can easy set a maxium.

Questions? No? Perfect.
Have a nice Day ^^

notes.title: Maximum Counter (GREEN)
notes.description:
Set a maximum for your channels.
Ex. 6 Channels are created then the "RED"-Channel should be closed for everyone.
Change it to your custom number.
